<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Evstafiev-Soviet-soldier-Afghanistan.jpg" class="image" title="Evstafiev-Soviet-soldier-Afghanistan.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/Evstafiev-Soviet-soldier-Afghanistan.jpg/300px-Evstafiev-Soviet-soldier-Afghanistan.jpg" width="300" height="200" border="0" /></a><br />
