<li id="cite_note-70"><b><a href="#cite_ref-70" title="">^</a></b> Hauner, M. (1989). Afghanistan and the Soviet Union: Collision and transformation. Boulder, Colorado: Westview Press. (p.40)</li>
<li id="cite_note-71"><b><a href="#cite_ref-71" title="">^</a></b> Barakat, S. (2004). <i>Reconstructing war-torn societies: Afghanistan. New York: Palgrave Macmillan</i> (p.5)</li>
