<li id="cite_note-73"><b><a href="#cite_ref-73" title="">^</a></b> Panetta L. (2007) <a href="/wiki/Collateral_damage" title="Collateral damage">Collateral damage</a> and the uncertainty of Afghanistan...<a href="http://www.soawne.org/CollateralDamage.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.soawne.org/CollateralDamage.html" rel="nofollow">[3]</a> San Francisco: OpticalRealities. Retrieved December 11, 2007</li>
